{"tid":2174782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳彥霖母親澄清沒有拒讓彥霖覆診 指醫生沒有主動詢問","createTime":"2020-08-26T06:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T07:25:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"253d37961ff14787aa82327e4ea0a5c418965047","tid":2174782,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:04:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/TSSDCVXN6NFGXKH65MNTRORM74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FTSSDCVXN6NFGXKH65MNTRORM74%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=a2399458\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FTSSDCVXN6NFGXKH65MNTRORM74%2F&h=9ba0dd15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/TSSDCVXN6NFGXKH65MNTRORM74/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾參與反送中集會的15歲職訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖，去年9月底離奇赤裸浮屍海面，警方及後指死因無可疑。死因裁判法庭就事件展開研訊，案件今天踏入第三天審訊。精神科醫生鍾加詠昨供稱，她去年8月21日致電陳母，告知彥霖患有「對立反抗症」，惟陳母拒絕帶彥霖覆診，陳母則在庭上指實是鍾表明彥霖不想覆診在先。今早甫開庭，陳母再次澄清，指當時鍾在電話表示彥霖稱聽到一把男聲，但拒絕覆診。陳母強調，鍾從未詢問她是否願意帶彥霖覆診，故自己沒主動拒絕，「醫生係專業，所以我相信佢」。"},{"pid":"88e4bf829270c884af32dfe9eda4ec9219f007b7","tid":2174782,"uid":59976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:07:16.000Z","msg":"支共最叻就係屈人精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9a5980d57f6b37219a8ce0ad6c598595a44c5d","tid":2174782,"uid":354682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街老母"},{"pid":"377ec3bc7c18a11d8db0849f6c60e760aaa40d47","tid":2174782,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc9a5980d57f6b37219a8ce0ad6c598595a44c5d","tid":2174782,"uid":354682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06